aplo-r:temporalExtent.Learner%20Elias.Ontology.Protege%20Ontology%20Editing.Protege%20Ontology%20Editing%20Revision%20State.2026-03-02T14%3A03%3A00Z%20to%202026-03-02T14%3A28%3A00Z a aplo-ont:TemporalExtent ;
